The KZN government’s plan to buy the Sapref oil refinery plant has been met with scepticism. Earlier this month, the country’s largest crude oil refinery announced its intention to halt operations by the end of March. eNCA’s senior reporter Dasen Thathiah has the details. #eNCA #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - The KZN government’s plan to buy the Sapref oil refinery plant has been met with scepticism. Earlier this month, the country’s largest crude oil refinery announced its intention to halt operations by the end of March. eNCA’s senior reporter Dasen Thathiah has the details.